## Korean translations for the auth surface (login, register, magic-link
## confirmation, the shared auth_split aside).
##
## #. TODO native-speaker review — anchors:
##   - "매직 링크" (magic link) — kept as Konglish; a Korean lawyer
##     reviewer may want "원클릭 로그인 링크" instead.
##   - "재인증" (re-authenticate) — chosen over "재로그인"; matches the
##     sudo-mode security framing.
##   - "비공개 베타" (closed beta) — already used on the landing page.
##   - Several brand-adjacent phrases ("Contract Studio", "법제처",
##     "R2 버킷") deliberately preserved verbatim.
